    "csaf_version": "2.0",
    "notes": [
      {
        "category": "summary",
        "text": "An update is available for webkit2gtk3.\nThis update affects Rocky Linux 8.\nA Common Vulnerability Scoring System (CVSS) base score, which gives a detailed severity rating, is available for each vulnerability from the CVE list",
        "title": "Topic"
      },
      {
        "category": "description",
        "text": "WebKitGTK is the port of the portable web rendering engine WebKit to the GTK platform.\n\nSecurity Fix(es):\n\n* WebKitGTK: use-after-free leads to arbitrary code execution (CVE-2023-28205)\n\nFor more details about the security issue(s), including the impact, a CVSS score, acknowledgments, and other related information, refer to the CVE page(s) listed in the References section.\n\nThis advisory is provided by Ctrl IQ, Inc for Rocky Linux systems. For more information about CIQ security practices, visit https://ciq.com/security.",
        "title": "Description"
      }
    ],
